---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" activeNav="about">

  <!-- ABOUT HERO -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-inner">
      <div class="about-hero-text">
        <span class="section-label">About David</span>
        <h1>Built for Complexity. Wired for Clarity.</h1>
        <p>
          I&rsquo;ve spent the better part of two decades helping executives and leadership teams
          navigate the moments that matter most &mdash; transitions, growth inflections, and
          the hard strategic decisions that don&rsquo;t come with a clear answer.
        </p>
        <p>
          My background spans strategy consulting, executive coaching, and organizational
          design across industries ranging from technology and healthcare to private equity
          and family-owned business. I bring the rigor of structured thinking with the
          warmth of a trusted advisor who&rsquo;s genuinely invested in your success.
        </p>
        <p>
          I believe the best advisory work happens when a leader stops feeling alone in
          the room. My job is to be that person for you.
        </p>
        <div class="about-hero-actions">
          <a href="/work-with-me" class="btn-teal">Work With David</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-teal-outline">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-hero-visual">
        <div class="photo-placeholder">
          <div class="photo-placeholder-inner">
            <span class="photo-initials">DL</span>
            <span class="photo-label">David Leder</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="credential-chips">
          <span class="chip">ICF Certified Coach</span>
          <span class="chip">Harvard Business School</span>
          <span class="chip">20+ Years Experience</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
  <section class="philosophy-section">
    <div class="philosophy-inner">
      <div class="philosophy-label">
        <span class="section-label">How I Work</span>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy-content">
        <h2>A Distinct Philosophy on Advisory Work</h2>
        <div class="philosophy-blocks">
          <div class="philosophy-block">
            <h3>Directness over diplomacy</h3>
            <p>
              Too many advisors tell clients what they want to hear. I&rsquo;m not that person.
              I ask the uncomfortable questions and say the things your team is too close
              to say. This only works if you want honesty &mdash; and most great leaders do.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="philosophy-block">
            <h3>Context over frameworks</h3>
            <p>
              I don&rsquo;t arrive with a pre-baked methodology. I listen first, deeply and
              without judgment. The right approach emerges from your actual situation,
              not from a framework I&rsquo;m trying to apply everywhere.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="philosophy-block">
            <h3>Progress over process</h3>
            <p>
              Advisory engagements fail when they become about the engagement itself. I
              measure success by what changes in how your team thinks, decides, and acts
              &mdash; not by the hours logged or decks delivered.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES GRID -->
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="values-inner">
      <div class="values-header">
        <span class="section-label">Core Commitments</span>
        <h2>What You Can Expect When Working With Me</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">&#9632;</div>
          <h3>Confidentiality</h3>
          <p>
            Everything shared in our work stays with me. No exceptions. The value of
            this space depends entirely on your ability to speak freely.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">&#9670;</div>
          <h3>Preparation</h3>
          <p>
            I come to every session having thought carefully about where we left off
            and what you might be navigating now. Your time is not for catching me up.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">&#9654;</div>
          <h3>Accountability</h3>
          <p>
            I hold you to what you said matters. Not as a task master, but because
            the whole point is forward motion &mdash; and drift is the enemy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INDUSTRY CHIPS -->
  <section class="industries-section">
    <div class="industries-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Industries Served</span>
      <h2>Breadth of Experience</h2>
      <p>
        Deep expertise in some areas, genuine experience in all of them. Cross-industry
        pattern recognition is one of the most undervalued things an advisor can bring.
      </p>
      <div class="industry-chips">
        <span class="industry-chip">Technology &amp; SaaS</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Healthcare &amp; Life Sciences</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Private Equity &amp; VC</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Financial Services</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Manufacturing</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Consumer &amp; Retail</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Family-Owned Business</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Professional Services</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Media &amp; Publishing</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Real Estate</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Non-Profit &amp; Education</span>
        <span class="industry-chip">Government &amp; Public Sector</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="cta-band-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Ready to Connect?</span>
      <h2>The Right Fit Starts With a Conversation</h2>
      <p>
        Advisory work is deeply personal. A 30-minute call is usually enough to know
        if there&rsquo;s a match &mdash; no pressure, no pitch.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <a href="/work-with-me" class="btn-white">Book a Call</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost">Send a Note</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: 140px 0 96px;
    background: var(--off-white);
  }

  .about-hero-inner {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-hero-text .section-label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-hero-text h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .about-hero-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .photo-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--navy) 0%, #2a4a70 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .photo-placeholder-inner {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .photo-initials {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .photo-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .credential-chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .chip {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--teal);
    background: rgba(42,127,127,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(42,127,127,0.2);
    padding: 5px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .philosophy-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .philosophy-inner {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .philosophy-label {
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  .philosophy-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .philosophy-block {
    padding: 32px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30,58,95,0.08);
  }

  .philosophy-block:first-child {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .philosophy-block:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .philosophy-block h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .philosophy-block p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .values-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--off-white);
  }

  .values-inner {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px;
  }

  .values-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .values-header .section-label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .values-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(30,58,95,0.07);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(30,58,95,0.09);
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    display: block;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .industries-section {
    padding: 96px 0;
    background: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .industries-inner {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px;
  }

  .industries-inner .section-label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .industries-inner h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .industries-inner > p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .industry-chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .industry-chip {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    background: var(--gray-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(30,58,95,0.1);
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .industry-chip:hover {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
    border-color: var(--navy);
  }
</style>
